database.name: Itikawa database
database.description: A set of recommended cross section data (angle integrated) for electron collisions with H2, N2, O2, CO, H2O, and CO2. The data are taken from the tables in the references listed for each species. The recommendations are based on available experimental data. In that sense, the present sets of cross sections are not complete. Uncertainty estimates are given in the references.
